    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191110/extras/3c5c69a167a352463cbb7a00c3123bc6.avif?t=1764226564\" width=960 height=400 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><i><strong>猫咪怪盗“亨迪”盗取了时间博物馆的时钟指针。​</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><i><strong>利用时钟指针的神秘力量，躲避无数警卫兵与无情的弹幕，从时间博物馆中杀出一条生路！​</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191110/extras/e65378941f5ba03554755ebdc9995178.avif?t=1764226564\" width=960 height=143 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191110/extras/1a7104db7bed94b5deb5ed62d7dab71d.poster.avif?t=1764226564\" width=680 height=380 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191110/extras/1a7104db7bed94b5deb5ed62d7dab71d.webm?t=1764226564\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191110/extras/1a7104db7bed94b5deb5ed62d7dab71d.mp4?t=1764226564\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">在生死攸关的瞬间，暂停时间躲避敌人的攻击，战略性地掌控局势。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">灵活运用时间暂停的能力，化解危机，把握胜利机会！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191110/extras/ed08347cafd42aa6d21a23005aaad1fa.avif?t=1764226564\" width=960 height=143 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191110/extras/1efc15a8d35e6b6a5fb01a03b058fa30.poster.avif?t=1764226564\" width=680 height=380 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191110/extras/1efc15a8d35e6b6a5fb01a03b058fa30.webm?t=1764226564\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191110/extras/1efc15a8d35e6b6a5fb01a03b058fa30.mp4?t=1764226564\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">游戏中的一切行动都会消耗“时间”，当时间耗尽时，时钟指针的神秘力量会将你带回到首次触碰它的那一刻。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">将体力、时间暂停的使用、道具购买等的唯一资源——</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">“时间”进行战略性管理，打败敌人收集“时间碎片”，延长你的逃脱机会！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191110/extras/744eb44f7e3ad78a006be12cf715fd3d.avif?t=1764226564\" width=960 height=143 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191110/extras/7e39ff8e867ccd5ecd01c939a9609bb3.poster.avif?t=1764226564\" width=680 height=380 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191110/extras/7e39ff8e867ccd5ecd01c939a9609bb3.webm?t=1764226564\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191110/extras/7e39ff8e867ccd5ecd01c939a9609bb3.mp4?t=1764226564\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">时间博物馆中不仅有时钟指针，还有各种展品！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">借用并组合博物馆各处展出的多种道具，创造强大的增益效果，让自己变得更强！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191110/extras/920059c0dc22a85323474e595379f528.avif?t=1764226564\" width=960 height=143 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191110/extras/b0dcb0dd60e2c584093b9effb5d80b2d.poster.avif?t=1764226564\" width=680 height=380 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191110/extras/b0dcb0dd60e2c584093b9effb5d80b2d.webm?t=1764226564\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191110/extras/b0dcb0dd60e2c584093b9effb5d80b2d.mp4?t=1764226564\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">逃脱博物馆越是近在咫尺，出现的敌人与首领就越强大。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">运用时间暂停的能力，以及一路借来的各种道具，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">突破每张地图中的各种机关和拥有独特攻击模式的敌人与首领，成功逃脱吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191110/extras/ff5de61208bde10c4b76270d309c514c.avif?t=1764226564\" width=960 height=143 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">时装不仅能让亨迪的外观更酷炫，还会带来独特的玩法变化。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">用最适合自己的玩法风格，攻略那些阻挡你逃出博物馆的敌人吧！</p>",
